<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/107903527-timothy-clancy"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/107903527-timothy-clancy">Timothy Clancy</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The negative effect colonialism had on modern Kenya and its people. That the sinister and powerful learned the art of subjugation from the white imper<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The negative effect colonialism had on modern Kenya and its people. That the sinister and powerful learned the art of subjugation from the white imperialists and applied it effectively. This book has an imaginary and somewhat fantastic scene where these evil doers meet to brag about their accomplishments in modern theft and robbery to one another and a panel of white foreigners. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
